data.description: *Back on market due to buyer cold feet, no inspections performed*    This 2 bedroom home in Belmont has been tastefully updated. The homes HVAC system and water heater was replaced in 2017, and the roof is NEW as of October 2023, so rest easy knowing the homes mechanics have been updated since the 1950s.     This cozy ranch with full basement has new flooring throughout with brand new carpet in the bedrooms. The living room is bright and inviting with a fireplace. The eat in kitchen has new black granite counters & white cabinets, with stainless steel appliances included, and the attached dining room is perfect for gatherings. The natural light illuminates the home during the day while the LED lighting provides efficiency throughout the evening. There is a full basement, framed & plumbed, perfect for storage, bonus rooms, or an office. The previous owner used it as a primary suite. There is also a one car attached garage for convenience, on street parking, and a fenced in yard to suit a multitude of needs.     Less than a mile from US-35, the possibilities are endless, whether you crave nightlife, restaurants, or a simple commute, this home checks all of the boxes.    Don't wait, schedule your showing today!
